Parliament, Sunday, 3 May 2020 – The Portfolio Committee on Tourism, and the Select Committee on Trade and Industry, Economic Development, Small Business Development, Tourism, Employment and Labour will tomorrow get a briefing from the Minister of Tourism on the impact of Covid -19 pandemic on the Tourism Industry, and the mitigating measures initiated by the department.
	
	Details of meeting:
	Date : Monday, 4 May 2020
	Time: 16:00 – 18:00
	
	To observe the meeting join Microsoft Teams Meeting
	Link to follow
	
	Members of the public may get involved and follow committee sittings live on Parliament TV (DStv Channel 408), via live stream on Parliament YouTube channel and Twitter page on the links below. You may subscribe to the Parliament YouTube channel to receive instant notification of live feeds.
	
